window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>This is a stand-alone novella set before the events of <i>Revenant Winds</i>. </p> <p>From Mitchell Hogan - Aurealis Award winner and author of the Sorcery Ascendant Sequence. </p> <p>Niklaus, master swordsman, has not aged a day since being chosen by his mercurial goddess. A slave to her will, he moves from one cryptic mission to the next in the hope of ascending to become her equal. </p> <p>But even a man who has lived for centuries can sometimes find himself out of his depth. </p> <p>When Niklaus is sent to kill a sorcerer of the Tainted Cabal, overconfidence leads to a fatal mistake, and neither experience nor skill with a blade can prevail against the forces unleashed against him. </p>"; 
